  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mobile Science Lab to Impact students in Zimbabwe</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Zimbabwe is promoting the uptake of Science subjects at A-level through the STEM programme. Makomborero has built and fully equipped a Mobile Science Lab (Biology) as our pilot project.  Converting a 20 foot container.  The Mobile Lab is now running at our Resource Centre, while we gain experience. This is giving students the opportunity to put their theoretical knowledge into practice through carefully chosen experiments. We need to raise money for the running costs.</narrative>
  </description>
